{"tid":2456842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<快訊> 台 灣 空 軍 2 架 F-5E 戰 機 墮 海","createTime":"2021-03-22T08:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T08:56:11.000Z","uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd706d358574991862a8678869ab4962a2124822","tid":2456842,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210322/JQLFA5LISJEAJAOI5CGJKU6UI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210322%2FJQLFA5LISJEAJAOI5CGJKU6UI4%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=3f612bfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210322%2FJQLFA5LISJEAJAOI5CGJKU6UI4%2F&h=7f6a2708\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210322/JQLFA5LISJEAJAOI5CGJKU6UI4/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7opUg4MjxYzJRZsNSXTXC2GIM2Y=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EUPFNMM53ND4DJL2LEBP5HVX2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7opUg4MjxYzJRZsNSXTXC2GIM2Y%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEUPFNMM53ND4DJL2LEBP5HVX2I.jpg&h=05aa2375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣再有戰機失事。2架屬於台東志航基地的F-5E戰機，今日下午3時18分從雷達上消失。戰機當時正在屏東旭海漁港上空飛行，疑經已墮海，當局馬上出動直升機前往現場搜救。軍方研判，兩戰機事發前曾可能發生擦撞，而兩名機師應已跳傘逃生。<br />\n<br />\n台軍F-5E戰機，是1974年由空軍航空工業發展中心與美國諾斯羅普飛機製造公司合作生產，機齡已超過45年，台灣軍方已規劃在2023至2026年，F-16V及新型高級教練機交付後，全面淘汰這些老舊戰機。<br />\n<br />\n然而，台軍的F-5E戰機過去曾發生多次事故，最近一宗發生在去年10月29日，一架同屬台東志航基地的F-5E戰機失去聯絡，當時軍方稱機師同樣跳傘逃生，但獲救時已沒有意識，搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果新聞網》/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"979e024e956629cb1c9c1744f683e22fad0e25bc","tid":2456842,"uid":90392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"最緊要機師無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06